Pickover5a{
;by Clifford Pickover, as given here http://rouxjeanbernard.ch/AM/html/amch82.html
init:
z=fn2(pixel)^@pow1
loop:
x=cabs(sin(p1*imag(z)))+(sin(p1*real(z)))^2
y=cabs(sin(p2*real(z)))+(sin(p2*imag(z)))^2
z=fn1(x+flip(y))^@pow2
bailout:
|z|<@bail
default:
