Kaplan-Yorke{
;https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=mbtCAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA56&lpg=PA56&dq=attractor+map&source=bl&ots=JE2mytSt6G&sig=OsISvZKKmhhqtBpB1krK74AvPkU&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiM29y_34PRAhWrLcAKHZGMCEs4FBDoAQgeMAE#v=onepage&q=attractor%20map&f=false
init:
z=fn1(pixel)
loop:
z=fn2(z)
x=p1*real(z)%1
y=-p2*imag(z)+cos(2*pi*real(z))
z=x+flip(y)
bailout:
